<br>
the 15 second DDs make a DRAMATIC difference in our dueling capability.<br>
<br>
unfortunately, as far as i can tell they have very little impact in what most of us care about, that being rvr.<br>
<br>
at this point if we are going to ask for something and actually expect to get it we need to be specific.  it needs to be group support, and it needs to have little impact on our ability to duel.  a good example of something like this would be the reaver's pbaedd chant.  that would be great to have, it would give us something to do in keeps and it would be a great to have 2 skalds in a group.<br>
